snippet.title: Metal: Hellsinger – The Gods of Metal Trailer
snippet.description:
Set out on an infernal journey in order to achieve the purest of goals: Vengeance in Metal: Hellsinger, an upcoming rhythm FPS game. Featuring some of your favorite metal artists including James Dorton, Matt Heafy, and now Randy Blythe from Lamb of God!

Coming 2022 for PC, Xbox Series X/S and PS5.

Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/3dTX8iO
Official Website: http://www.metalhellsinger.com

Follow us on the official social media channels to never miss a beat
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/metalhellsinger
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/metalhellsinger
